FlashFunders Funding Portal LLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg




































































  









Feedback























flashfunders funding portal llc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Asset Management
Sub-Industry: Investment Companies
FlashFunders Funding Portal, LLC operates as a crowdfunding online portal. The Company assists entrepreneurs, developers, and operators to raise capital through securities offerings to a pool of individual investors online.




Corporate Information
Address:

1538 20th Street
2nd Floor
Santa Monica, CA 90404
United States


Phone:
1-310-504-3706


Fax:
1-310-504-3704


Web url:
www.flashfunders.com























