FlashFunders | Raise Capital With Equity Crowdfunding

























We're currently onboarding companies, sign up to see when investments go live.









Thank you for subscribing to FlashFunders Insider.






















Raise Capital. The Right Way.











Raise Up to $50 Million from The Crowd



+






Raise Unlimited Funds from Accredited Investors



+






Raise Unlimited Funds from International Investors




Apply Now




How it Works










Onboard your company
Work with our investment team to build your offering. We'll review your company's materials and build your offering page with you.










Market your Round
Engage investors in as many ways as possible. Use PR, social media, email campaigns, and meetings to round up the capital you need.










Close your Deal
Accept your investments countersign documents, prepare regulatory forms, and receive funds from the offering deposit account or escrow.










Grow your Business
Once you've received your capital, keep investors up to date on your progress. Keeping investors informed will position you for successful future fundraising.








What We Offer






Tools and Services to Build a Compelling Pitch
Pitch Editor
Tell your story with our pitch editor. Your offering hub will include everything you need to pitch to the entire world online, including a product page, video, assets and team overview.
Legal Onboarding
Work with onboarding specialists to prepare all your fundraising documents. We provide investment document templates, conduct background checks, and establish an offering deposit or escrow account for you to make your round compliant. Your onboarding and offerings will be handled by either our broker dealer or funding portal.







Analytics and Communication Tools to Promote Your Round
Dashboard
Keep track of who your investors are, their locations, and their investment progress with comprehensive analytics. Understand what works in your marketing campaign, and what doesn't, as you monitor investment activity from your dashboard in real time.
Investor Communications
Answer questions in a forum-style comments section that creates transparency in your offering. Get notified instantly when investors request an introduction. We also provide the email address of any registered user who has engaged with your offering page, so you can convert them into shareholders.







Streamlined Deal Execution
Investor Verification
If accredited investors participate in your offering, our broker dealer will verify that they meet SEC requirements. Our broker dealer also conducts customer identification program (CIP) and anti-money laundering (AML) procedures to monitor proper handling of your funds.
Regulatory Compliance
Our broker dealer or funding portal will file your SEC forms, Blue Sky forms, and/or articles of incorporation on your behalf, and assist with all the other legal documents necessary to close your round in a compliant manner.







Ongoing Post-Fundraising Investor Management
FlashFunders Shareholder Services
We support you after the deal is done. FlashFunders Shareholder Services, LLC is an SEC-registered transfer agent that electronically records all your investors' shares in book-entry format, should you elect to utilize their services. We maintain an organized record of your cap table, manage all inbound investor requests and help disseminate your annual financial reports.


